name: User tries to purchase CWS at store with Mobile Payments and Car Wash subscriptions and no CWS features in native BU
description: CWS flow when at a store with no car wash at native BU
descriptionHtml: CWS flow when at a store with no car wash at native BU

testStage.description: CWS flow when at a store with no car wash at native BU

steps.name: I check that the Saucelabs session is preserved

parameters.name: userProfile
parameters.value: {PHONE_NUMBER=782782000, FIRST_NAME=Kamil, PASSWORD=#Test123, EMAIL=kamil.nowak@gmaptest.com, PHONE_COUNTRY_PREFIX=+48, PHONE_COUNTRY=Poland, OTP=000000, LAST_NAME=Nowak, BUSINESS_UNIT=DK}

steps.name: I skip linking my card
I mock the location of the device to "DENMARK_NO_CAR_WASH"
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I check that the "Profile" tab is displayed
I click on "BUILD NUMBER" tab
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I enter the location data of the "DENMARK_NO_CAR_WASH" station
I check "Set Location" page is visible
I enter the site ID "DENMARK_NO_CAR_WASH" in the input
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I click on "Car Wash" advertisement
I check if "Car Wash" advertisement is displayed
I close and open application
I make sure that the location is set correctly
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I check that the "CAR WASH" tab is displayed
I click on "CAR WASH" tab
I make sure that the "CAR WASH" tab is in the default state
I click on Car Wash "BEGIN CAR WASH" button
I check that the "No Car Wash here" is displayed
I check that the "NEAREST CAR WASH" label is displayed
I check the number of "Nearest station" on the list
I check that the actual value: "3" is greater or equal than value "3"
I get Nearest Store name List
I check that the application text: "Nørrebrogade 12-14" is equals to expected value: "Nørrebrogade 12-14"
I get Nearest Store name List
I check that the application text: "Vesterbro 1" is equals to expected value: "Vesterbro 1"
I get Nearest Store name List
I check that the application text: "Kalundborgvej 130" is equals to expected value: "Kalundborgvej 130"
I get Nearest Store distance List
I check that the application text: "90.4 km" is equals to expected value: "90.4 km"
I get Nearest Store distance List
I check that the application text: "118.6 km" is equals to expected value: "118.6 km"
I get Nearest Store distance List
I check that the application text: "122.4 km" is equals to expected value: "122.4 km"
I click on "GO BACK" button
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
